Speaker 2: And in light of all this, bud, I want to apologize to you about this profusely because even what—

Speaker 1: But I adjusted it to 10.

Speaker 2: That way it's not a lot when you decide.

Speaker 2: A 30-day period and no less than 20 pills a year, but you did that many times over.

Speaker 1: So whenever you're ready, just go ahead and click that or call me.

Speaker 2: My extension, Gary, is 0037.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: And just keep in mind because the pills are good for five years, but if for some reason—

Speaker 1: Your body gets anti-climatic or you get some adverse side effects, because the body changes—

Speaker 2: As you know, call me and I'll give you a replacement, okay?

Speaker 1: We always back our product, all right, bud?

Speaker 2: Always here for you, right, bud?

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: Sounds good, man.

Speaker 1: All right, bud.

Speaker 2: You take care.

Speaker 1: And you should leave the money there, bud.

Speaker 2: You take care, bud.

Speaker 1: Much love.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: You too.

Speaker 2: Appreciate it.

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: Adios.

Speaker 1: You bet.
